text: Vincent Adams (born 26 January 1950) is a British Guianese cricketer. He played five first-class matches for Guyana between 1968 and 1975. ==See also== * List of Guyanese representative cricketers ==References== ==External links== * Category:1950 births Category:Living people Category:Guyanese cricketers Category:Guyana cricketers
